\id GAL - Ndendeule Bible Version
\h Akagalatiya
\toc1 Baluwa jha Pauli kwa Akagalatiya
\toc2 Akagalatiya
\toc3 Akag
\mt2 Baluwa jha Pauli kwa
\mt1 Akagalatiya
\imt1 Ulongolelo
\ip Baluwa kwa bhando bha ku Galatiya jhijhandikwe na ntenga Pauli, mu chula jha 1:1. Na ikajhandikwe na Pauli kwa makunde gha bhando bhibhannyeketii Kilichitu bhibhabhii ku Galatiya pakate jha chaka cha makome ncheche na nane ade makome nhwano na chaba pabhelwikwa njwe Yecho Kilichitu. Pange Akagalatiya bhatamita kubomane jha ku Galatiya jhibhii chehemo jha ulongoche gwa Kiloma. Bhando bhubhachomite bhakwetejhe uchakaka panane jha chehemo jha Pauli kojhe pajhandikila baluwa jhenje, pange akibha ku muche gwa ku Epecho amu ku Kolintu.
\ip Pauli akajhandikile baluwa jhenje kwa bhando bhoha bhibhannyeketii Kilichitu kwa Akayahude na bhangebhehe Akayahude na makunde gha bhando ghighannyeketii Kilichitu gha kwenio ku Galatiya. Chakaka baluwa jhenje akajhandike kughakana mabholo ghuwange ghighalongela bhando bhibhannyeketii Kilichitu bhaghakengame kwa Akayahude kubhoka mulilaghano lya Makacho, akachokolikii hake achwa kujhingii jando. Pakate jha bhando bhibhannyeketii Kilichitu pakibha na likunde limo lilikemitwa Akayuda, bhando bhamba bhachokolikiya bhando bha ilambo henge bhajhingile jando. Helahela bhando bheniya bhakonyita machwale twe panane jha ukindendeke gwa Pauli. Pauli akengilila utenga gwake kwa kulonge luhomo lwake lumo, mu chula jha 1:11-2:14, na alikengilila Lilobhe lya Mbone kwa kulonge kubhehe bhando bhahoto kukombolelwa kwa kuhobholela Yecho Kilichitu kanjika, mu chula jha 2:16. Lijhambu uletwa na umbone ghulangiwa na Chapanga na chi kuhenga mundo.
\iot Ghughabhii mukitabo
\io1 Pauli itumbuu baluwa jhake kwa kwajhambucha makunde gha bhando bhibhannyeketii Kilichitu bha Ku Galatiya, mu chula jha 1: 1-5.
\io1 Pauli ichimulila malobhe ghake jwenio chakibha kwenio kunyuma na kone akengilila kupala kwake kubhola na kulangiya kubhehe akajhighite kutama kwa kukengama lilaghalikilo, nambo lijhambu lijhakulepelela, mu chula jha 1:6-2: 21.
\io1 Pauli ichimulila hake chikihengwa na lilaghaliho na umbone gwa Chapanga mu ughombokeko, mu chula jha 3-4.
\io1 Pauli apiya machimulilo ghange gha kulangiya chibhapalwa kutama bhando bhibhannyeketii Kilichitu, mu chula jha 5-6:10.
\io1 Pauli ikutila mu baluwa jhake kwa kwajhambucha bhando na kwalobholela bhakomboke kubhehe kughalambulwa na Chapanga na kutendwa ihumbe inhyono ndi kilebhe chamaha hake kuliku lilaghalikilo lya panja anda hela kujhingii jando, mu chula jha 6:11-18.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nenga Napauli, ngemitwe jhe hilu ndumitwe jhe na mundo kubhehe natenga, nambo ngemitwe na kutumwa na Yecho Kilichitu na Chapanga Tate gwito jwakayokiche Yecho Kilichitu kuhumii mu kuwegha,
\v 2 nenga na akalongo bhoha bhibhabhii pamonga na nenga tunyandikila mangota makunde gha bhando ghighannyeketii Kilichitu gha ku Galatiya.
\p 
\v 3 Ninyope umbone na uteeke kuhumii kwa Chapanga Tate gwito na Bhambo Yecho Kilichitu.
\p 
\v 4 Yecho Kilichitu akajheketile kuwe jwenio kwa nhwalo jha uhakaho gwito twenga ngita chapalita Chapanga Tate gwito, atukombole kuhumii mu nnema ghongo gwanganandela gwa ngohe.
\v 5 Chapanga abhii na ung'alicho machiko ghoha ghangapeta! Amina.
\s1 Libhii Lilobhe lya Mbone limo tugha
\p 
\v 6 Nikangacha munneka Chapanga kajhombekajhombe, jwahaghuline mangota kwa umbone gwa Kilichitu, na nkengime lilobhe lenge lilibhonekana ngita Lilobhe lya Mbone.
\v 7 Chakaka libhii jhe Lilobhe lenge lya Mbone. Nongi yenio, nhwalo bhabhii bhando bhibhamubhoghana, na bhapala kulighalambula Lilobhe lya Mbone lya Kilichitu.
\v 8 Nambo anda mundo pakate jhito amu ntumiche jwa kunane kwa Chapanga, natangachila lilobhe lenge lya mbone chi ngita lituntangachii twenga, bhahe, jwenio abhaha na likoto!
\v 9 Ngita chinongolile kulonge, na ngohe nibhujhii kabhele kulonge, anda mundo jhojhoha anobholile Lilobhe lya Mbone lenge na chi lela lipokile, jwenio abhaha na likoto lya Chapanga!
\p 
\v 10 Bho, nipala kunhalalicha ghane? Bho, nipala kunhalalicha mundo amu Chapanga? Anda ngandenda yenio, ngangundike ng'o nenga kubhehe natumiche jwa Kilichitu.
\s1 Pauli chakemitwa na Chapanga
\p 
\v 11 Makalongo bhango, mbala umanye kubhehe Lilobhe lya Mbone lindangicha lela lihumii jhe kwa bhando.
\v 12 Hilu nenga mbokii jhe kuhumii kwa mundo jhojhoha amu nikabholitwe jhe na mundo. Nambo Yecho Kilichitu jwenio ndi jwayekulile gheniya.
\p 
\v 13 Mangota mukajhohine punikibha makacho pungamwila dine jhango jha Kiyahude, na chinang'ahita makunde gha bhando bhibhanyeketii Kilichitu nambata kwakomelekeya njwe.
\v 14 Chakaka, nenga nikachochite hake mu dine jha Kiyahude kuliku Akayahude twe bhitulenganii yaka nhwalo ng'aghita hake kughakamula mabholo ghala gha akanahota bhito.
\p 
\v 15 Nambo Chapanga, kwa umbone gwake akahagwii nakubhelukwa jhe, angemite niunhengele mahengo.
\v 16 Pala tugha payekulila Mwana mundo nkate jhango, ndangache Lilobhe lya Mbone kwa bhando bha ilambo henge, nikabhutwiki jhe kunkonya mundo jhojhoha.
\v 17 Helahela nikajhawii ndeka ku Yeluchalemo kwa bhala bhibhakalongalile kubhehe akatenga, nikatumbwii kujhenda ku Alabiya, peniya nyakukelebhuka kabhele ku Damasiko.
\v 18 Puipetita yaka itato nyakuhobhoka ku Yeluchalemo kukongana na Petile, nyakutama nako kwa machiko kome na nhwano.
\v 19 Nambo nikakonganike jhe na ntenga jhonge jhojhoha nga Yakobu, unung'una mundo Bhambo Yecho.
\p 
\v 20 Chenje chinijhandika ndi chakaka, Chapanga amanye, nilonge uwange jhe.
\p 
\v 21 Bhahe, machiko gha palongolo nyakujhenda ku kilambo chuku Siliya na ku Kilikiya.
\v 22 Machiko gheniya, namwete bhanamona jhe makunde gha bhando ghighanyeketii Kilichitu gha ku kilambo chuku Yudeya kola.
\v 23 Chibhakimanyite bheniya ndi chela chikilongelwa na bhando: “Mundo jhola jwatung'ahita makacho, ngohe atangachii bhando Lilobhe lya Mbone lelela lela lya kuhobholela Kilichitu lyapata kulikomelekeya!”
\v 24 Yene, bhajhakunnomba Chapanga kwa nhwalo jha nenga.
\c 2
\s1 Pauli na akatenga bhange
\p 
\v 1 Peniya, puipetita yaka kome na ncheche, nyakuhobhoka kabhele kujhenda ku Yeluchalemo pamonga na Banaba, helahela nyakulongohana pamonga na Titu.
\v 2 Kujhenda kwango ngita chakayekulile Chapanga nyende. Pantemela kwenio ku Yeluchalemo nikakongine na ilongoche, nikalobholile Malobhe gha Mbone ghinatangachila bhando bha ilambo henge. Ndehila naha nipala lihengo lyango lindehila likoto kubhehe jhajhe.
\v 3 Nambo Titu jwakalongohine pamonga na nenga, pamo na kubhehe Nghilike, akachokolikiwe jhe kujhingii jando,
\v 4 pamonga na kupitii akalongo bhuwange bhibhapata ajhingii jando. Bhando bhamba bhajhakukiwininika kwa kuchenjela bhalingulile chitutama kwa uteeke mu kulombana na Kilichitu Yecho, bhatutende akabhanda,
\v 5 nambo tukajheketii jhe kwa kupala hilu lichaa limo uchakaka gwa Lilobhe lya Mbone liighalike kwino mangota.
\p 
\v 6 Nambo bhando bhamba bhibhamanyikana pange ilongoche, anda bhakibha ilongoche amu ilongochejhe, kwale bhene. Nhwalo gwa Chapanga ihadabuu jhe kwa kulolekeya ilebhe ya panja. Bhando bhamba bhakwete jhe mabholo gha kunyonjekeya nenga mu mabholo ghango.
\v 7 Chibhakimanye, Chapanga angamwii lihengo lya kutangacha Lilobhe lya Mbone kwa bhando bha ilambo henge, anda jhe Petile chatumitwe kwatangachii Lilobhe lya Mbone kwa Akayahude.
\v 8 Nhwalo jhola jwatangatila Petile kubhehe ntenga jwa Akayahude, ndi jhojho jwandangatii nenga helahela kubhehe natenga kwa bhando bha ilambo henge.
\v 9 Yene, Yakobu na Kefa na Yohane ndi bhabhoneka kubhehe ilongoche ikolongwa, bhakaumanye Chapanga ambekiye umbone ghongo. Tujhakukamulana mabhoko na twenga, hote Banaba na nenga, kulangii nginyililo tubhii pamonga. Twenga tughakamwii mahengo pakate jha bhando bha ilambo henge na bhange bhajhende kwa Akayahude.
\v 10 Nambo ngabhatujhopita kilebhe chimo, kwakomboka akahocho, na nenga ndi ng'aghita hake kilebhe chenie.
\s1 Pauli ipwatalii Petile ku Atiyokiya
\p 
\v 11 Nambo Petile pahikita ku Antiyokiya, ngatahungina nako hotuhotu palonge jha bhando, nhwalo akatei kulemwa.
\v 12 Kabula jha kuhika bhando bhibhakatumitwe na Yakobu, Petile alila pamonga na bhando bha ilambo henge. Nambo pubhahikita bhando bheniya, ajhakuhila na akalii ng'o na bhando bha ilambo henge, nhwalo ajhogwipa bhando bhala bhibhachokolikiya kujhingii jando.
\v 13 Akayahude bhange bhakibha ndela jhimo kwa Petile patehila kilebhe ngita chambone, na jwenio Banaba ujhakunhuta umbebhebhe gwenio.
\v 14 Bhahe, punolita ndela yabhe ilandana jhe na uchakaka gwa Lilobhe lya Mbone, nyakunobholela Petile palonge jha bhando bhoha: “Pamonga mwenga ndi Mayahude, mitama ngita Mayahude, na kone chi Mayahude. Nhwalo gwa nike mwachokolekeya bhando bha ilambo henge bhakengame mabholo gha Kiyahude?”
\s1 Akayahude na bhando bha ilambo henge nabhakombolelwa kwa kihobholelo
\p 
\v 15 Twenga ndi Akayahude njwe kwa kubhelukwa, na chi bhando bha ilambo henge bhibhabhii na uhakaho.
\v 16 Nambo tumanya mundo ihotojhe kubhalangilwa jwaumbone palonge jha Chapanga nhwalo alijheketile Lilaghalikilo lya Mucha, nambo tugha kwa kunnyeketila Yecho Kilichitu. Na twenga hele tunyeketile Yecho Kilichitu tuteilwe tubhalangilwe na Chapanga twaumbone kwa ndela jha kujheketela kwito na Kilichitu, na chi kwa kuhenga chilipala Lilaghalikilo. Nhwalo abhii jhe mundo jwatendwa jwaumbone palonge jha Chapanga kwa kukamula Lilaghalikilo lya Mucha.
\v 17 Nambo anda twenga tupala, kutendwa tubhonekana twaumbone palonge jha Chapanga kwa kulombana na Kilichitu, twenga twabhete tubhonekana tubhii na uhakaho. Bho, ngoheno kilebhe chenie kibhonekana Kilichitu abhatangatila bhando kuhenga uhakaho? Nahi jhe!
\v 18 Nhwalo anda nichenga kabhele kwa lijhambu lela lilihobholela lilaghalikilo lihangabhine, bhahe, ilangii nenga nemwite.
\v 19 Nhwalo gwa Lilaghalikilo lyenio nenga hwile, Lilaghalikilo lyenio lingomite na nandama ghome kwa nhwalo gwa Chapanga. Nenga mambitwe pamonga na Kilichitu panchalaba,
\v 20 na ngoheno namite, ne jhe kabhele, nambo Kilichitu jwabhii nkate jhango. Ughome ghongo ghumii nako ngoheno nitama kwa ndela jha kunhobholela Mwana gwa Chapanga, jwenio jwambahile na jwakapihite ughome gwake kwa nhwalo gwango.
\v 21 Nikana jhe umbone gwa Chapanga. Anda mundo atendwa jwaumbone palonge jha Chapanga kwa kujheketela Lilaghalikilo, yenio Kilichitu akahwii jhajhe!
\c 3
\s1 Kihobholelo na Lilaghalikilo
\p 
\v 1 Mangota bhando bhu ku Galatiya mandindililma! Bho, ghane jwannoghite mangota? Malobhe gha kubhambwa panchalaba kwa Yecho Kilichitu ghalongilwe hotuhotu palonge jha miho ghino!
\v 2 Mbala manye kilebhe chimo. Bho, ngohe mukapokile Uhuke gwa Chapanga kwa nhwalo gwa kukamuu Lilaghalikilo lya Mucha amu kwa kuijhokanikiya na kulihobholela Lilobhe lya Mbone?
\v 3 Bho, mangota mandindilima naha? Mangota mukalongolile kuhenga ghoha kwa Uhuke gwa Chapanga, bho, ngohe mipala kujhomolela kwa makakala ghino mabhene?
\v 4 Bho, mang'ahiko ghing'ahika ghakibha jhajhe? Chakaka ghakibha jhajhe ndeka!
\v 5 Bho, Chapanga akatwelii Uhuke gwake na kuhenga ikangacho pakate jhino nhwalo mujheketela Lilaghalikilo lya Mucha amu nhwalo mujhoha na kujheketela Lilobhe lya Mbone?
\p 
\v 6 Mukibhole nnandanikiho gwa Ulahimo, ngita chighalonge Majhandiko gha Chapanga, “Jwenio akannyeketile Chapanga, na kwa nhwalo gwa kujheketela kwake akabhonike jwaumbone palonge jha Chapanga.”
\v 7 Ngohe umanye kubhehe bhala bhoha bhibhanyeketela Chapanga, bheniya ndi yana ya Ulahimo.
\v 8 Nhwalo Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghakalongolile kulonge kuhumii makacho bhando bha ilambo henge nabhabhalangilwa bhaumbone kwa ndela jha kihobholelo. Yene Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghakalongolile kuntangachii Ulahimo Lilobhe lya Mbone, “Kupete mwenga bhando bhoha nabhapokela mota.”
\v 9 Yene, bhando bhoha bhibhanyeketela Chapanga bhapokii mota pamonga na Ulahimo, jwajheketile Chapanga.
\p 
\v 10 Nhwalo bhoha bhibhahobholela kulenganikiya chilipala Lilaghalikilo, bhitama pahe jha likoto. Nhwalo Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghilonge, “Abhii na likoto lya Chapanga mundo jhola jwangakamuu na kuhenga ghoha ghighajhandikwe mukitabo cha Lilaghalikilo!”
\v 11 Ngohe makalongo bhango, abhii jhe mundo jwabhalangilwa jwaumbone palonge jha Chapanga kwa kukamuu Lilaghalikilo, nhwalo Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghilonge, “Mundo jwaumbone kwa Chapanga natama kwa kihobholelo.”
\v 12 Nambo Lilaghalikilo nalijhema jhe mu kihobholelo, ngita chighalonge Majhandiko gha Chapanga, “Mundo jhojhoha jwaikamuu Lilaghalikilo nabhaha ghome kwa kupete Lilaghalikilo lyenio.”
\p 
\v 13 Kilichitu akatughombwii kuhumii mulikoto lya Lilaghalikilo, na jwenio ajhakutola likoto lyenio kwa nhwalo gwito, Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghilonge, “Abhii na likoto mundo jhojhoha jwabhambitwe pa nchalaba.”
\v 14 Kilebhe chenie kitendika naha mota jhela jwakapokii Ulahimo jhahikila bhando bha ilambo henge kwa ndela jha Kilichitu Yecho. Na kwa ndela jha kihobholelo, tupokii Uhuke gwa Chapanga jhola jwatulaghila Chapanga.
\s1 Lilaghalikilo na lilaghano
\p 
\v 15 Makalongo bhango, nanimpela nnandanikiho kuhumii mughome gwito gwa machiko ghoha. Bhando bhabhele pibhajhomolela kulaghana na kujheketelana kwa kulapilana, abhii jhe mundo jwahoto kuhangabhana amu kujhonjekeya kilebhe mu majheketelano gheniya.
\v 16 Ngohe, Chapanga akabhekite lilaghano kwa Ulahimo pamonga na ibheluko yake, Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghilonge ndeka, “Na ibheluko yake,” yane bhando twe, ghilonge, “Ndi kibheluko chake ndo,” yane jhumo, na jwenio ndi Kilichitu.
\v 17 Kilebhe chimbala kulonge ndi chenje, Chapanga akabhekite lilaghano lyake na Ulahimo na akalongile chahenga ngita chalaghine nako. Kuhumii muyaka miya ncheche na makome matato palonge lijhakuhika Lilaghalikilo, dola lihoto jhe kulighalambula lilaghano hilu kulitwekula lilaghano lyenio.
\v 18 Nhwalo anda hupo ya Chapanga ihobholela Lilaghalikilo lya Mucha, bhahe, ihoto jhe kuhobholela kabhele lilaghano lya Chapanga. Nambo Chapanga kwa umbone gwake ajhakumpeke mota Ulahimo kupete lilaghano lyenio.
\p 
\v 19 Bho, ngohe Lilaghalikilo libhii na lihengo ghane? Lilaghalikilo libhekitwe kulangiya malemo. Na lyenio likajhendelii ade pahikita jhola kichokolo cha Ulahimo mu lilaghano lyenio. Lilaghalikilo likaletitwe na ntumiche jwa kunane kwa Chapanga kwa lubhoko lwa nnyelanicha.
\v 20 Nambo chakaka, jwajhelanicha nakemwa jhe anda kilebhe chenie kimpala mundo jhumo ndo, nambo Chapanga ndi jhumo.
\s1 Lihengo lya Lilaghalikilo
\p 
\v 21 Bho, Lilaghalikilo lijhenda uhenga mbopo na lilaghano lya Chapanga? Nahi jhe! Nhwalo Lilaghalikilo lilipihitwe ngalihotwii kwapeke bhando ughome, bhahe, bhando ngabhabhalangilwe bhaumbone palonge jha Chapanga kwa ndela jha Lilaghalikilo.
\v 22 Nambo, Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghalongii bhando bhoha bha pannema ulongochwa na uhakaho, ndi bhala bhibhanyeketila bhalenganikilwe lilaghano lela lyapihita Chapanga, kwa kunyeketela Yecho Kilichitu.
\p 
\v 23 Nambo pala kihobholelo na kuhika jhe, tukibha mukipungo cha Lilaghalikilo, kone tulendila kihobholelo chenie kiyekulilwe.
\v 24 Bhahe, Lilaghalikilo litulongwicha ade pahikita Kilichitu, kwa ndela jha kihobholelo tubhalangilwe twaumbone palonge jha Chapanga.
\v 25 Nhwalo gwa kihobholelo chito kihikite, tulongochwa jhe na Lilaghalikilo.
\p 
\v 26 Kwa ndela jha kihobholelo, mangota mabhoha ndi mayana ya Chapanga kwa kulombana na Kilichitu Yecho.
\v 27 Mangota bhubatichwe na kulombana na Kilichitu, muwalite Kilichitu jwenio.
\v 28 Kwa gheniya, kibhii jhe chikilekine pakate jha Uyahude na Nghilike, pakate jha mmanda na mundo jwangabhehe mmanda, pakate jha munalome amu mwikeghe. Nhwalo mabhoha uyokite kilebhe chimo kwa kulombana na Kilichitu Yecho.
\v 29 Anda mangota ndi mabhando bhake Kilichitu, ngohe mangota ndi kibheluko cha Ulahimo, mangota nampokela chela chalaghii Chapanga.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Nenga mbala kulonge naha, nniche pabhehe amela mwana, ilekenii jhe na mmanda kone ilebhe yoha yake.
\v 2 Kipinde chenie choha ulongochwa na bhando bhibhannela na bhando bhiakalonda ilebhe yake ade kipinde chela chikibhekwite na tate mundo pukipala kuhika.
\v 3 Na twenga helahela putukibha na kukomala jhe ki uhuke, tukibha twakabhanda bha uhuke ghulongocha nnema ghango.
\v 4 Nambo pukihikite kipinde chamaha, Chapanga ajhakuntuma Mwana mundo jwapapitwe na mwikeghe, ngatamita pahe jha Lilaghalikilo lya Kiyahude,
\v 5 abhakombole bhala bhando bhibhabhii pahe jha Lilaghalikilo, ndi twenga tubhehe yana ya Chapanga.
\p 
\v 6 Nhwalo mangota ndi yana ya Chapanga, nhwalo mangota ndi mayana nhwalo akatumite Uhuke gwa Mwana Mundo mu miojho jhito, na Uhuke jwenio alelita, “Aba,” mana jhake, “Tate.”
\v 7 Yene, mangota makabhanda jhe kabhele, nambo ndi mayana. Anda mmii mamwana, bhahe, nampokela yoha yalenganikiye Chapanga kwa yana mundo.
\s1 Kiholo cha Pauli kwa Akagalatiya
\p 
\v 8 Makacho mukibha mumanyite jhe Chapanga, na yenio mukibha mubhanda kwa ihumbe yangabhehe ichapanga, nambo Chapanga jwa chakaka jhe.
\v 9 Nambo ngohe mmanye Chapanga, anda jhe mmanyikana na Chapanga, nahotola bhole kughabhujhila kabhele mabholo ghighalongalile ghangabhehe na makakala na ghapengwa na mipala ghantende mme akabhanda bhake?
\v 10 Dola mwamela mughakamwii machiko na miyehe na yaka!
\v 11 Nipwelela pange lihengo lihengita kwino mangota ndi lihengo lya jhajhe!
\p 
\v 12 Makalongo bhango, ninyopangana mme ngita nenga, ngita hela nenga mii ngita mangota. Utendii jhe kilebhe chochoha changanandela.
\v 13 Mikomboka malwalo ghango pumbatita pwache jha kutumbuu kuntangachii Lilobhe lya Mbone mangota.
\v 14 Pamonga na gheniya, machiko ghala mukambuchite jhe amu kungana nhwalo gwa kulegheleka kwango ikibha majhighanikilo kwino. Nambo ngaumbokila ngita natumiche jwa kunane kwa Chapanga amu ngita Kilichitu Yecho jwenio.
\v 15 Mukibha ku mwojho jhojwa! Bho, ngoheno kipitii kilebhe ghane? Nilapii kwa machiko ghala ngahotwii kukotopola miho ghino na kumbeke nenga.
\v 16 Bho, ngohe mindenda nalikoko kwa nhwalo gwa kunnongolela ukwele?
\p 
\v 17 Bhando bheniya bhapalaha kunnyonja mangota, nambo mawacho ghabhe ghambone jhe. Bhapala kutulekanicha mangota na nenga, bhapala mangota makengame bheniya.
\v 18 Chakaka kilebhe chambone machiko ghoha kwapata bhando bhange, na chi pumme pamonga na mangota tujhe.
\v 19 Yana yango, ngita chilebhehe lipyanda lya majhe jhuna ndumbo papala kupapa, na nenga hele mii na lipyanda kabhele ade Kilichitu puipala kupanganwa nkate jhino.
\v 20 Nikapahi kubhehe na mangota ngohe, nganongii na mangota kwa namuna jha umanye hotuhotu! Nhwalo nimpwelii hake mangota!
\s1 Nnandanikiho gwa Hagale na Sala
\p 
\v 21 Ngohe unobholele mangota bhumipala kulongochwa na Lilaghalikilo lya Mucha, bho, mukajhohine jhe chililongila Lilaghalikilo?
\v 22 Nhwalo ijhandikwe mu itabo ya Malaghalikilo, Ulahimo akapapite yana ibhele. Jhumo kwa mwikeghe mmanda na jhonge jwangabhehe mmanda.
\v 23 Jhola mwana jwabhelwike kwa mwikeghe mmanda akabhelwike ngita bhando chibhabhelukwa, nambo mwana jhola jwa mwikeghe jwangabhehe mmanda akabhelwike kwa lilaghano lya Chapanga.
\v 24 Mambu gheniya ghamanyikana ngita nnandanikiho, kwa akamajhe bheniya bhalangii malaghano mabhele. Lilaghano lya kutumbula ndi lya mwana jwa Hagale bhubhabhelwike mubhanda lilitendike pa kitombe chuku Sinae.
\v 25 Hagale alenganichwa na kitombe cha Sinae chikibhii ku kilambo chuku Alabiya, na ndi ulandine na Yeluchalemo jha ngohe, jhibhii mubhanda pamonga na yana mundo.
\v 26 Nambo Yeluchalemo jha kunane kwa Chapanga ndi muche gwangabhehe pahe jha ubhanda, na jwenio ndi majhe gwito.
\v 27 Nhwalo ijhandikwe mu Majhandiko gha Chapanga,
\q1 “Nhanganile mwe jhumii mantonga!
\q1 Unonoye lilobhe kululuta mwe mangapapa mwana!
\q1 Nhwalo yana ya mwikeghe jwalibhalilwe jhola ibhii twe
\q1 kuliku mwikeghe jhola jwatolilwe.”
\p 
\v 28 Ngohe makalongo bhango, mangota ndi ngita chalaghine na Chapanga ngita chabhii Isaka.
\v 29 Nambo ngita hela kwa machiko ghala kwa mwana jhola jwakabhelwike ngita bhando chibhabhelukwa ajhakung'aha mwana jhola jwabhelwike kwa makakala gha Uhuke gwa Chapanga, na machiko ghanga ibhii hele.
\v 30 Nambo Majhandiko gha Chapanga ghilonge bho? Ghilonge, “Mumenge mwikeghe mmanda na mwana mundo, nhwalo mwana jha mmanda nabhujhii jhe na mwana jwa mwikeghe jwangabhehe mmanda.”
\v 31 Yene makalongo bhango, twenga chi yana ya mwikeghe mmanda, nambo ndi yana ya mwikeghe jwangabhehe mmanda.
\c 5
\s1 Kilichitu atutehi tukoto kubhehe akapungwa
\p 
\v 1 Bhahe, Kilichitu atutehi kubhehe akabhanda. Ngohe nnyeme nganganga, mangajheketela mu lingolengole lya ubhanda kabhele.
\p 
\v 2 Unyokanikiye mbone! Ne Napauli jhunilonge na mangota anda nnyeketile kujhingii jando, Kilichitu kibhii jhe najhambulila kwino.
\v 3 Nilonge hotuhotu kabhele, mundo jhojhoha jwajheketii kujhingii jando akamule Malaghalikilo ghoha.
\v 4 Anda milolela kubhalangilwa maumbone palonge jha Chapanga kwa ndela jha Lilaghalikilo, bhahe, mmii kutale na Kilichitu, nambo mukanite umbone gwa Chapanga.
\v 5 Nambo twenga, tulendelela kwa lihobholelo lito kwa likakala lya Uhuke gwa Chapanga, tutendwe twaumbone palonge jha Chapanga kwa kihobholelo.
\v 6 Nhwalo tulombine na Kilichitu Yecho, kujhingii jando amu changajhingii jando kilebhe nacho, nambo kilebhe chambone ndi kihobholelo chikihenga lihengo kwa upalo.
\p 
\v 7 Mukibha nteila maha! Bho, ngohe ghane jwahibhilikiye nkotoka kujheketela ukwele?
\v 8 Jwatehi kilebhe chenie Chapanga ndeka jwakemita mangota.
\v 9 “Amila jhandina jhihotwii kuumula ukobha ghoha!”
\v 10 Nhwalo tulombine na Bhambo, nihobholela mangota namme jhe na mawacho ghighajhepana na nenga. Kabhele mundo jwenio jwamwoghana, abhe mundo jhojhoha jhola, chakaka nachwapulwa na Chapanga.
\p 
\v 11 Makalongo bhango, ngita chinijhendelela kwatangachii bhando bhajhingii jando, bho, nhwalo ghane ngohe Akayahude bhang'aha naha? Anda ibhii yenio, kwatangachii kwango malobhe gha nchalaba gwa Kilichitu ngabhayomite Akayahude.
\v 12 Ngaibhii mbone kwa bhando bheniya bhibhamoghana, mbaha bhakihekete bhene!
\p 
\v 13 Mangota makalongo bhango, nkemitwe nkotoka kubhehe bhando bhangatabhwa. Nambo kilebhe chenie kikoto kubhehe kikopokeo cha kuhenga chochoha chimukipala, nambo mipalwa kuhengelana kwa upalano.
\v 14 Nhwalo Lilaghalikilo lyoha litimile kwa nhwilo ghongo: “Mupale nnyino ngita chimukipala mabhene.”
\v 15 Nambo milumana na kumemenana ngita inyama, mukilolokeye nkoto kukocholana mabhene kwa mabhene.
\s1 Ughome ghulongochwa na Uhuke gwa Chapanga
\p 
\v 16 Ngohe nilonge naha: Ntamengane kwa kulongochwa na Uhuke gwa Chapanga, nambo mangota nankengama jhe kabhele mambu gha pannema ghighapala yegha.
\v 17 Nhwalo mambu gha pannema ghijhelana jhe na Uhuke gwa Chapanga, helahela Uhuke gwa Chapanga ujhelena jhe na mambu gha payegha. Mambu ghanga mabhele ghitama jhe pamonga, yenio mihoto jhe kuhenga chochoha chimipala mabhene.
\v 18 Ngohe mulongochwa na Uhuke gwa Chapanga, mujhendelela ng'o na Lilaghalikilo.
\p 
\v 19 Bhahe, mambu ghighatendwa na yegha ghamanyikana njwe, ngongola na uhakata na kulongochwa na kupala kuhenga ilebhe twe,
\v 20 kujhinamii inyagho na uhabhe na ulikoko na milomo na wiho na lilaka na chojho na lung'wenyo na mpechengano,
\v 21 lingele na kulobhela na kuhutilwa kutenda ilebhe yakiteno na ilebhe henge iwanana ngita yenio. Ninobholela kabhele ngita chininongolila kunobholela, bhando bhibhatenda yenio nabhajhingii ng'o mu Unahota nkolongwa gwa Chapanga.
\p 
\v 22 Nambo mundo jwalongochwa na Uhuke gwa Chapanga abhaha na upalo na luhangano na uteeke na luhimba na umbone na mwojho gwa kupiya na kuhobholeka,
\v 23 utokomalo na kukilongocha jwenio. Libhii jhe Lilaghalikilo lilikana mambu ghanga.
\v 24 Bhando bhoha bhibhalombine na Kilichitu Yecho bhaghakomite mawacho ghabhe na mambu ghanganandela ghughakibha nkate jhabhe.
\v 25 Nhwalo tutama kwa kulongochwa gwa Uhuke gwa Chapanga, helahela tuneke alongoche ughome gwito.
\v 26 Bhahe, tukotoka kukiloka na tukoto kubhehe na milomo amu kukolelana wiho.
\c 6
\s1 Tuimbililane na kutangatana
\p 
\v 1 Makalongo bhango, anda mundo alemwite chakiteno, mangota bhimulongochwa na Uhuke gwa Chapanga munkelebhuwa mundo jwenio kwa utokomalo. Nambo mukilolekeya mabhene nkotoka kujhingii mu majhighanikilo.
\v 2 Ntangatana mu malagho ghino, kwa kuhenga yenio mutimicha Lilaghalikilo lya Kilichitu.
\v 3 Anda mundo akibhona kilebhe, kone kilebhe nacho, mundo jwenio akikopokeya jwenio.
\v 4 Nambo kila mundo akilingukiya jwenio chahenga. Anda chambone, bhahe, ahoto kukilokela nkate jhake changakilenganicha na chahenga mundo jhonge.
\v 5 Nhwalo kila mundo nahadabulwa kwa chela chateile.
\p 
\v 6 Mundo jwabhola Lilobhe lya Mbone lya Chapanga apalwa abhaghana ilebhe yoha yamaha na mmola gwake.
\p 
\v 7 Mangakoloana, Chapanga mangantendela chanake. Chamichite mundo ndi chahuna.
\v 8 Mundo jwamicha mambu ghanganandela ghighabhii nkate jhake, nahuna kuwegha, nambo jwamicha kwa kunhalalicha Uhuke gwa Chapanga, jwenio napata ughome gwa chakaka machiko ghoha ghangapeta.
\v 9 Ngohe tuko kutotokela kuhenga ghambone, nhwalo anda tuhengelike jhe mwojho natuhuna mahuno kwa kipinde chake.
\v 10 Ngohe kila putubhehe na pwache, twatendele ghambone bhando bhoha, ichocha kwa bhando bhibhabhii mu kihobholelo cha Kilichitu.
\s1 Malobhe gha kujhomolela na nyambucho
\p 
\v 11 Nnolekeye chinyandike kwa nembo ngolongolo, kwa lubhoko lwango namwete!
\v 12 Bhando bhoha bhibhapala bhabhonekane bhaumbone kwa ilebhe ya payegha ndi bhibhanchokolekeya mangota kujhingii jando. Bhahenga yenio kwa nhwalo bhakoto kulagha kwa nchalaba gwa Kilichitu.
\v 13 Nhwalo ata bheniya bhibhajhingii jando bhalikamwii jhe Lilaghalikilo lya Mucha, nambo bhapala mangota nnyingii jando bhalolekele huna jhene jhibhii payegha jhino.
\v 14 Nambo nenga kibhii ng'o chinikilokela, nambo nikilokela nga nchalaba gwa Bhambo gwito Yecho Kilichitu, nhwalo kwa nchalaba nnema ukibha ngita uhwile kwa nhwalo jhango, na nenga ngita hela hwile panane jha nnema.
\v 15 Kwa nhwalo kujhingii jando amu changajhingii jando kibhii jhe chikijhonjekeya, chikipalwa ndi kubhehe kihumbi kihyono.
\v 16 Bhando bhoha bhibhahobholela gheniya Chapanga abhapeke uteeke na kiya, helahela kwa Akaichilahele na bhando bhoha bha Chapanga!
\p 
\v 17 Kuhumii ngohe mundo jhojhoha angoto kundotowa kabhele, nhwalo mabhanga ghighabhii payegha jhango nhwalo nenga nabhanda jwa Yecho Kilichitu.
\p 
\v 18 Makalongo bhango, umbone gwa Bhambo gwito Yecho Kilichitu utame na mangota mabhoha. Amina.
